  "_narrative": "**Where We Stand**\nWe're tied for first in Pool C with everyone at 0 points, as no games have been played yet. Rankings have us second in the pool behind #3 Kincardine, but we're here to compete.\n\n**Our Next Game**\nWe face the Ennismore Eagles on Friday April 10th at 9:15 AM. Rankings suggest we match up well against the #25 Eagles, but they'll come out hungry and anything can happen in tournament hockey.\n\n**Around the Pool**\nAt the same time as our game, Kincardine takes on Windsor in what should be a mismatch on paper. We win the pool in 156 out of 729 possible scenarios based on how the remaining games could play out, showing we have multiple paths to first place if we take care of business.",
